Body shamers, go suck a stinky sock. Have turned off comments cause I’m not looking for words of comfort etc. What I wished I’d known as a teenager: Bullies do it because putting others down boosts their own ego / it makes them feel better about themselves. YOU are awesome and whoever is saying horrid things to you can get in the bin.

Life is so precious, hug them 🖤 I’ve lived longer without him than with, but the sometimes the pain of losing this rockstar creeps up on me and feels like day 1, when I found out. Today is that. Today, on the anniversary of losing my Dad, I’ve been reading some of the letters from the Words Unspoken project on @suicideandco website and have never felt more understood. To anyone that’s listening- you’re not alone, and you are loved. Do things that make you happy, be silly, eat loads of tasties and don’t keep whatever you’ve got going on bottled up.
Lately 🌸 bits from home and afar
Kefalonia on film- the last pictures I took before my camera was stolen. 🫠 Goodbye Mju 1

THE LONG SHADOW trailer has arrived - airing this month on ITV 1 and ITV X. @itv @itvxofficial 

Directed by the brilliant Lewis Arnold @lewisaea with the most stunning cast. An honour to be reunited with @katherinekel and alongside the likes of Toby Jones, Daniel Mays and my gorgeous and talented pals @officialmarcusfraser, @rebecca.hanssen @moflowright and @natgav004

It was an honour to join this incredible ensemble, The Long Shadow - starting this Monday 25th Sept at 9pm on @itv @itvxofficial 

Directed by the brilliant @lewisaea and written by George Kay, this 7 part series follows the atrocious crimes of Sutcliffe, the lives and loss of the women, of those left behind, the enormity of the wave felt across Yorkshire & Nationally and the 5 year manhunt between 1975-1980. The Long Shadow is delivered with sensitivity, grace and outstanding talent, everyone involved in this production is a true diamond. 

Sending love to you all, look after one another 💛
All episodes of The Long Shadow are now available to stream / binge on @itvxofficial or you can watch weekly on @itv 1, Mondays at 9pm. 🖤🤍🖤
